{"id":852,"parent_id":828,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":852,"title":"Ezekiel 24","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ezek.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 24"],[".studySummary",["i","The irrevocable judgment of Jerusalem is foretold—As a sign to the Jews, Ezekiel does not weep at his wife’s death."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.1","order":"02.27.024.56795"},["b","1"],"Again in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"ninth"],"year, in the tenth month, in the tenth",["i","day"],"of the month, the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.2","order":"02.27.024.56796"},["b","2"],"Son of man, write thee the name of the day,",["i","even"],"of this same day: the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"king"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"Babylon"],"set himself against Jerusalem this same day."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.3","order":"02.27.024.56797"},["b","3"],"And utter a parable unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"rebellious"],"house, and say unto them, Thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Set on a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"pot"],", set",["i","it"],"on, and also pour water into it:"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.4","order":"02.27.024.56798"},["b","4"],"Gather the pieces thereof into it,",["i","even"],"every good piece, the thigh, and the shoulder; fill",["i","it"],"with the choice bones."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.5","order":"02.27.024.56799"},["b","5"],"Take the choice of the flock, and burn also the bones under it,",["i","and"],"make it boil well, and let them seethe the bones of it therein."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.6","order":"02.27.024.56800"},["b","6"],"¶Wherefore thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Woe to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"bloody"],"city, to the pot whose scum",["i","is"],"therein, and whose",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"scum"],"is not gone out of it! bring it out piece by piece;",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"let"],"no lot fall upon it."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.7","order":"02.27.024.56801"},["b","7"],"For her blood is in the midst of her; she set it upon the top of a rock; she poured it not upon the ground, to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"cover"],"it with dust;"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.8","order":"02.27.024.56802"},["b","8"],"That it might cause fury to come up to take vengeance; I have set her blood upon the top of a rock, that it should not be covered."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.9","order":"02.27.024.56803"},["b","9"],"Therefore thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Woe to the bloody city! I will even make the pile for fire great."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.10","order":"02.27.024.56804"},["b","10"],"Heap on wood, kindle the fire, consume the flesh, and spice it well, and let the bones be burned."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.11","order":"02.27.024.56805"},["b","11"],"Then set it empty upon the coals thereof, that the brass of it may be hot, and may burn, and",["i","that"],"the filthiness of it may be molten in it,",["i","that"],"the scum of it may be consumed."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.12","order":"02.27.024.56806"},["b","12"],"She hath wearied",["i","herself"],"with lies, and her great scum went not forth out of her: her scum",["i","shall be"],"in the fire."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.13","order":"02.27.024.56807"},["b","13"],"In thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"filthiness"],["i","is"],"lewdness: because I have purged thee, and thou wast not purged, thou shalt not be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"purged"],"from thy filthiness any more, till",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"I"],"have caused my fury to rest upon thee."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.14","order":"02.27.024.56808"},["b","14"],"I the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"have spoken",["i","it:"],"it shall come to pass, and I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"do"],["i","it;"],"I will not go back, neither will I spare, neither will I repent; according to thy ways, and according to thy doings, shall they judge thee, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.15","order":"02.27.024.56809"},["b","15"],"¶Also the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.16","order":"02.27.024.56810"},["b","16"],"Son of man, behold, I take away from thee the desire of thine eyes with a stroke: yet neither shalt thou mourn nor weep, neither shall thy tears run down."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.17","order":"02.27.024.56811"},["b","17"],"Forbear to cry, make no",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"mourning"],"for the dead, bind the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"tire"],"of thine",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"head"],"upon thee, and put on thy shoes upon thy feet, and",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_17d"},"cover"],"not",["i","thy"],"lips, and eat not the bread of men."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.18","order":"02.27.024.56812"},["b","18"],"So I spake unto the people in the morning: and at even my wife died; and I did in the morning as I was commanded."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.19","order":"02.27.024.56813"},["b","19"],"¶And the people said unto me, Wilt thou not tell us",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"what"],"these",["i","things are"],"to us, that thou doest",["i","so?"]],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.20","order":"02.27.024.56814"},["b","20"],"Then I answered them, The word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.21","order":"02.27.024.56815"},["b","21"],"Speak unto the house of Israel, Thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Behold, I will profane my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"sanctuary"],", the excellency of your strength, the desire of your eyes, and that which your soul",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"pitieth"],"; and your",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"sons"],"and your daughters whom ye have left shall fall by the sword."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.22","order":"02.27.024.56816"},["b","22"],"And ye shall do as I have done: ye shall not cover",["i","your"],"lips, nor eat the bread of men."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.23","order":"02.27.024.56817"},["b","23"],"And your tires",["i","shall be"],"upon your heads, and your shoes upon your feet: ye shall not mourn nor weep; but ye shall pine away for your iniquities, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"mourn"],"one toward another."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.24","order":"02.27.024.56818"},["b","24"],"Thus Ezekiel is unto you a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"sign"],": according to all that he hath",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"done"],"shall ye do: and when this cometh, ye shall know that I",["i","am"],"the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.25","order":"02.27.024.56819"},["b","25"],"Also, thou son of man,",["i","shall it"],"not",["i","be"],"in the day when I take from them their strength, the joy of their glory, the desire of their eyes, and that whereupon they set their minds, their sons and their daughters,"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.26","order":"02.27.024.56820"},["b","26"],["i","That"],"he that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"escapeth"],"in that day shall come unto thee, to cause",["i","thee"],"to hear",["i","it"],"with",["i","thine"],"ears?"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.27","order":"02.27.024.56821"},["b","27"],"In that day shall thy mouth be opened to him which is escaped, and thou shalt speak, and be no more",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"dumb"],": and thou shalt be a sign unto them; and they shall know that I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.1a","order":"02.27.024.56822"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/25.1"},"2 Kgs. 25:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/39.1"},"Jer. 39:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/52.4"},"52:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/1.2"},"Ezek. 1:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.21"},"33:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.2a","order":"02.27.024.56824"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/39.1"},"Jer. 39:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.2b","order":"02.27.024.56826"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/10.3"},"1 Ne. 10:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.3a","order":"02.27.024.56828"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/44.6.6-7"},"Ezek. 44:6 (6–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.3b","order":"02.27.024.56830"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/1.13.13-14"},"Jer. 1:13 (13–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.6a","order":"02.27.024.56832"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/blood-shedding-of"},"TG Blood, Shedding of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.6b","order":"02.27.024.56834"},["b","6b"],["span.small","OR"],"refuse or filth."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.6c","order":"02.27.024.56836"},["b","6c"],["span.small","IE"],"let none of the pieces be selected for consecration."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.7a","order":"02.27.024.56838"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/17.13"},"Lev. 17:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.13a","order":"02.27.024.56840"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/filthiness"},"TG Filthiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.13b","order":"02.27.024.56842"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/13.27"},"Jer. 13:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/128.24"},"D&C 128:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.13c","order":"02.27.024.56844"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.13"},"Ezek. 5:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.14a","order":"02.27.024.56846"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.17"},"2 Ne. 9:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.17a","order":"02.27.024.56848"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/16.5.5,7"},"Jer. 16:5 (5, 7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.17b","order":"02.27.024.56850"},["b","17b"],["span.small","HEB"],"headdress (turban).",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/33.4"},"Ex. 33:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.17c","order":"02.27.024.56852"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/10.6"},"Lev. 10:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"17d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.17d","order":"02.27.024.56854"},["b","17d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/13.45"},"Lev. 13:45"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.19a","order":"02.27.024.56856"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/12.9"},"Ezek. 12:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/37.18"},"37:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.21a","order":"02.27.024.56858"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/7.14"},"Jer. 7:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.22.21-22"},"Ezek. 7:22 (21–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.21b","order":"02.27.024.56860"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/103.13"},"Ps. 103:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"21c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.21c","order":"02.27.024.56862"},["b","21c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/23.47"},"Ezek. 23:47"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.23a","order":"02.27.024.56864"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/7.24"},"Mosiah 7:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/9.22"},"Hel. 9:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.24a","order":"02.27.024.56866"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/12.6"},"Ezek. 12:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.24b","order":"02.27.024.56868"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/12.11"},"Ezek. 12:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.26a","order":"02.27.024.56870"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.21.21-22"},"Ezek. 33:21 (21–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/24.27a","order":"02.27.024.56872"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.26.26-27"},"Ezek. 3:26 (26–27)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.22"},"33:22"],"."]]}
